 29→    /// Add a phase audit record to the current run.
 30→    ///
 31→    /// Returns an error if no run is currently active (i.e., `start_run` was never called
 32→    /// or `finish_run` has already been called). This prevents silent data loss when callers
 33→    /// forget to start a run before logging phase data.
